Thanks for the report @brianegan!

I should have this one fixed coincidentally w/ some performance improvements in 3b8131b07e78de07f4fe0404feb80a2cbc6b2e76.  Closing optimistically (and this code path is gone now to boot).  Will keep an eye out for other related issues though.

Cheers!
Sounds great, thanks! I'll reopen if I see it again with the next version.
